title: Missing dll when running on Windows
body:
#### System information

Erigon version: 2022.02.04-beta

OS & Version: Windows 10

#### Expected behaviour

Trying to start Erigon with or without a datadir flag

#### Actual behaviour

The program does not start, with Windows reporting that libgcc_seh_seh-1.dll was not found.
Cleaning and recompiling did not solve the issue.

#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour

Compile Erigon using the wmake file and start Erigon.exe
